blog.description: Lauren. But you can call me LO. I’m just your average Taylor Swift loving (ok love her more than the average person), Jesus Loving, Sauvignon Blanc drinking 29 year old. summary: Only redeeming part about a Monday morning is getting to put this up at my desk and tell everyone how amazing and impactful...
caption: Only redeeming part about a Monday morning is getting to put this up at my desk and tell everyone how amazing and impactful Reputation Stadium Tour Atlanta was. First concert I was able to afford and attend (because i had to support myself through college) since i was 18 years old and it was worth the wait.  @taylorswift you made me laugh, cry, whoop it up. You’re amazing sis. cc: @taylornation

summary: I love this fandom, I really do but people are really out here like “JOE PUT HIS PROFILE OFF PRIVATE SO TAYLOR COULD LIKE HIS...

I love this fandom, I really do but people are really out here like “JOE PUT HIS PROFILE OFF PRIVATE SO TAYLOR COULD LIKE HIS STUFF…” you know their love is real and so there is much more to their relationship than social media and her being able to like his photos… actually the last thing those two are worried about is liking each other’s posts.

it just makes me laugh a little 😊
